            </details>

            <details>
                <summary class="sum2">
                    Left Rotate
                </summary>
                
                <p>
                    Let's enter 2, 4, 6 in the:
                    <br />
                <a
            href="https://www.cs.usfca.edu/~galles/visualization/RedBlack.html">
                        Red-black tree visualizer
                    </a>
                </p>
                
                <p>
                Here's the pseudo-code:
                <code>
                <pre>
                Left-Rotate(T, x)
                    y = x.right
                    x.right = y.left
                    if y.left != T.nil
                        y.left.p = x
                    y.p = x.p
                    if x.p == T.nil
                        T.root = y
                    elif x == x.p.left
                        x.p.left = y
                    else
                        x.p.right = y
                    y.left = x
                    x.p = y
                </pre>
                </code>
                </p>
            </details>

        </details>


        <details>
            <summary class="sum1">
                13.3 Insertions
            </summary>

            <details>
                <summary class="sum2">
                    Insert Animation
                </summary>

                <figure>
                    <iframe width="560" height="315"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vDHFF4wjWYU"
                        frameborder="0" allowfullscreen>
                    </iframe>
                    <figcaption>
                    A series of insertions in a red-black tree
